snippet.title: Bubumbu - Trailer
snippet.description:
Bubumbu is a game in which the player helps lost items find their way back to where they belong. The game consists of a variety of hand-drawn mini-worlds filled with secrets and wacky characters.

Obtenlo/Get It/ Obtê-lo: https://anotterteam.itch.io/bubumbu

Redes/Socials/Redes Sociais: https://twitter.com/AnOtterTeam
